  "title": "Loans Admin Executive (Motor Vehicle)",
  "description": "<p><strong>Benefits Summary:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Up $3500 + Variable Bonus</li>\n  <li>5 Days work week</li>\n  <li>Working Location: East</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Responsibilities:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Verification of supporting documents received from customers, to ensure that documents are complete and comply with the regulatory and banks’ requirements</li>\n  <li>Work closely with the Sales team to ensure there are no pending, aged cases</li>\n  <li>Assist to notify and follow-up with external parties (banks, customers etc.) on outstanding cases</li>\n  <li>Process and submit loan disbursements to bank partners promptly and accurately</li>\n  <li>Any ad-hoc duties as required</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Interested candidates, please submit your updated resume in MS format by using the <strong>Apply Now</strong> Button.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Text us on <strong>WhatsApp</strong> for more details:<br>\nhttps://wa.me/6582693981</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Our dedicated and approachable E&amp;C consultants will get back to you soon for a confidential discussion.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>By submitting your application or resume to us, you will be deemed to have agreed and consented us that we may collect, use or disclose your personal information for purpose in connection with the services provided by us.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>**We regret to inform that only shortlisted candidates would be notified. **</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Han Zhe CHUNG<br>\nRegistration No: R22107943<br>\nEA License No: 20C0278</p>",
